Also, the Gigabyte GA586ID is PCI/EISA.  Comparing the Buslogic 747C (EISA)
and their PCI version with the same Seagate Barracuda 2.1GB SCSI drive
showed performance in the same ballpark, although I didn't do extensive
testing on this.  

